Section 6: Dealing with Integration and Batch Processing
### Lecture 6.4: CQRS (Command Query Responsibility Segregation

* CQRS
  * CQRS stands for Command Query Responsibility Segregation
  * At scale, same mental model for queries and for update does neither well
  * Define bounded contexts for domain
  * Use messaging to propagate changes to query models between domains (microserivces)
  